21:
Aaah! You're wearing that outfit
again!
25:
I-I don't wear it that often! And
Arum! I thought I told you to knock
before you—
27: What was that scream just now?!
36:
D-d-doesn't anyone here know how
to knock?!
40:
S-sorry! I thought something
happened, so I just—
I'll leave right away!
49:
Huh? "The Oculus Times Special
Edition: Your Guide to Palpebra's
Anniversary Festivities."
66:
What are you looking at?!
Sixteen-year-olds read this sort of
stuff all the time, don't they?! Then it
shouldn't be an issue!
73:
What, you got something to say
about that?
79:
Hmph, good. Anyway, if you're free,
you should help me out.
85:
*munch* Mmm, this place is good
too. Which do you think is better, this
shop or the third one?
88:
You're planning to go out with Phiria
and Cecilia, right? In that case... This
place might be better... I think.
93:
Got it... Alright, now let's go over the
afternoon course.
97:
Wait... Are we going to check out all
the spots you found in the Oculus?
101:
O-of course. Those girls have been
so nice to me, so it's only fair that I
return the favor!
103:
And if I'm gonna be the one inviting
them out, I have to make sure it's
perfect...
107:
But I hardly ever go out for fun, so I
have no idea what to do...
111:
Got it. Don't worry, we'll help. I'll even
show you a few places I know—
117: Whoa, wait, what are you doing?!
123:
I believe that's Phiria and Cecilia.
Perhaps they are also here to
peruse the shops.
141:
I'm a fiend. I shouldn't force myself
into their little human circle. They're
better off without me...
144:
But wasn't Phiria the one who asked
you to be friends?
148:
...She was probably just being polite.
Besides, she's not exactly a typical
human either...
152:
Hmm, but you won't know for sure
unless you ask, right?
159: Huh?! Wait, what are you doing?!
169: Why is he bringing them here?!
178:
N-no reason! Just a big
coincidence, that's all!
183:
These two were just checking out a
few places they wanted to invite you
to.
195:
Well, this is rather embarrassing...
You see, we're not very
well-acquainted with these sorts of
activities...
205:
Well, now that you're all here, why
don't you three hang out?
210:
Huh?! B-but... I'm not mentally
prepared... I haven't finished my
resear—
214:
Come on, going in without a plan
can be pretty fun, you know.
228:
Um, well, in that case... There's a
store I want to check out... Would
you like to come?
